brands.brand: the american dj f-timer-dyno ii is an optional timer remote for dyno-fog ii fog machine. it controls the fog output at designated time intervals. three led lights indicate different functions: yellow - timer is turned on and is activated red - power is on green - fog output is available the remote features dual rotary knobs that turns the timer on and off and setting the length of fog output.
